entries.femaleVariant: Goddamn, stuck again... C'mere, help me out.
[Open]
Press there, a little to the left... Yep, that's it.
Holy shit, Mitch... What the hell?!
Relax, V. It's what Scorpion wanted.
He wanted you to stuff him in the trunk like a spare tire?
If that's what he wanted...
Saul won't be mad about this?
Saul won't like this. Blasting a good car... Terrible waste.
entries.maleVariant: Saul won't like this. Blastin' a good car... It's a terrible waste.

entries.femaleVariant: I'll tell him it was an accident.
I mean, if that's what Scorpion wanted...
He did. Said it a million times if he said it at all.
[Pick up gas can]
Here you go.
Great. Go ahead, put it in the passenger seat.
[Place can]
See the driver's already behind the wheel...
entries.maleVariant: I see the driver's already behind the wheel...

entries.femaleVariant: No point wasting time. Another hour or two, and he'll puff up like a balloon.
Let's do this thing.
You sure this is a good idea?
You absolutely sure this is a good idea?
entries.maleVariant: Are you absolutely sure this is a good idea?

entries.femaleVariant: No, V. No, I am not.
Let's do it.
Hell yeah. I've already got a rag in the can. You light it, I'll start the car.
[Light]
She's burning! Quick, before she blows!
Out with a bang. Just like he wanted.
Soot and ash. That much remains.
Sure. I'll drink to a send-off like that.
Sure thing.
So... How about a beer?
I gotta go.
Sorry... Wakes aren't really my thing.
Well, come on.
Aaaah... Nothing like a good cold one.
Agreed.
[Take]
What is it?
Not a clue... Scorpion always had it on him. No idea why.
Listen... I'm going to sit here for a while, all right? Brood in peace.
No. He wanted me to take him here... and send him off with a bang.
We set him up behind the wheel, douse the car... then light it, let him fly off the edge.
You're out of your goddamn mind!
Mitch. You've fucking gonked.
Yeah, yeah, quit complaining.
Grab me that can, will you?
Right. Shall we get this show on the road?
But it was my best friend's dying wish. So I'll do whatever the fuck I can to make it happen. With or without you.
Welp, that's your loss.
Hey, V! Thanks. I appreciate it.
Mitch – why me? Why'd you ask me to help?
Why'd you ask me to help?
Where'd "Scorpion" come from?
Hey, speakin' of... Where'd that nickname come from? "Scorpion"?
Funny... You know, I haven't the slightest idea. Never asked him.
He a Scorpio or somethin'?
Heh – maybe he had a big stinger, hehehe!
Ah, Scorpion, you old bastard... I'm 'onna miss you, man.
Eh, you seem like a good egg.
I'm serious.
I don't know, I uh... I guess the fact that I'm still here to send him off right – that's thanks to you.
Your paths crossed. Just for a moment... But damn, was it the right one.
Listen, there's a... a few things of his you oughta have. Like this little good luck charm. Go on, it's yours.
Understood. I'll be off, then.
entries.maleVariant: Understood. I'll, uh... I'll be off, then.

entries.femaleVariant: Oh, and, uh... thanks, V. For today... And for getting me out of that shit back then, too.
You're all right. You're really all right.
Nothing for me, thanks.
No, thanks. Rather keep things sober.
All right, my city choom... everyone grieves their own way.
If you say so.
Sure. Listen, if you want, you can take my car back to camp. Whatever works for you.
May the road be kind to ya, friend.
You lost your damn mind?!
V... the can. What are you waiting for?
Let's do this, V. For Scorpion.
Go ahead, light it!
C'mon. It's what he wanted.
Cat got your tongue?
Hey, no need for a moment of silence just yet.
You still with us, V?
